  "introduction": "Failure is often misinterpreted as a definitive end or a character flaw, yet it is merely a pivot point in the journey of growth. We tend to fear the stumble more than we embrace the lesson hidden within the fall. By shifting our perspective, we can transform disappointment into a powerful catalyst for resilience and innovation.",
